The encoded dictionary that used the flower and political cream of Prague during the previous period, of Mayor Pavel Bém, includes some of the most well-known characters, situations and causes of the metropolis.
Surprisingly, it has been found that the new councillors hardly understand these well-known concepts.
At least that's what they say.
"Who's Voldemort?"
